OL,3,CTeenager admits taking two knives into
OL,4,Ca school and stabbing a pupil
OL,6,FA 15-year-old from Nottingham has
OL,7,Fadmitted taking two knives into a
OL,8,Fschool and stabbing a pupil with one
OL,9,Fof them.
OL,11,FThe teenager appeared at Nottingham
OL,12,FCrown Court on Wednesday, May 27.
OL,14,FHe plead guilty to wounding with
OL,15,Fintent to cause grievous bodily harm
OL,16,Fand possession of a serrated knife and
OL,17,Fa kitchen knife on school property.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
