OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1779948269
OL,3,CTeenager admits taking two knives into
OL,4,Ca school and stabbing a pupil
OL,6,FThe teen, from The Meadows, carried
OL,7,Fout all three offences at Nottingham
OL,8,FUniversity Academy of Science and
OL,9,FTechnology (NUAST) in Dunkirk just
OL,10,Fafter 1.30pm on Thursday, March 5.
OL,12,FHis identity is protected by law due
OL,13,Fto his age.
OL,15,FNottinghamshire Police officers
OL,16,Fattended the school after reports of
OL,17,Fan assault and a 15-year-old boy was
OL,18,Fseriously injured.
OL,20,FThe boy was arrested at the scene and
OL,21,Fwas later charged.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
