PN,37503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1779948269
OL,3,CTeenager admits taking two knives into
OL,4,Ca school and stabbing a pupil
OL,6,FDefence barrister Lucky Thandi
OL,7,Finitially asked for a 12-week
OL,8,Fadjournment so that a psychological
OL,9,Freport and a separate report from the
OL,10,Fyouth offending team could be prepared
OL,11,Fahead of sentence.
OL,13,FBut Judge Nirmal Shant KC, Honorary
OL,14,FRecorder of Nottingham, told her she
OL,15,Fwas not prepared to wait that long to
OL,16,Fsentence someone as young as the teen.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
