PN,37504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1779948269
OL,3,CTeenager admits taking two knives into
OL,4,Ca school and stabbing a pupil
OL,6,FAdjourning instead to July 20, she
OL,7,Ftold the teenager: "You have now
OL,8,Fpleaded guilty and obviously that
OL,9,Fmeans you accept you have committed
OL,10,Fsomething very serious.
OL,12,F"You have to know this means the court
OL,13,Fwill put you in a position where you
OL,14,Fwill not have your freedom for some
OL,15,Ftime."
OL,17,FNottinghamshire Police previously said
OL,18,Fthat although the victim was initially
OL,19,Ftaken to hospital with a stab wound,
OL,20,Fhis injuries were not believed to be
OL,21,Flife-threatening.
