OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1779948269
OL,3,CTeenager admits taking two knives into
OL,4,Ca school and stabbing a pupil
OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector Chris
OL,7,FBerryman previously said: "This
OL,8,Fincident has understandably been
OL,9,Fdeeply upsetting for students,
OL,10,Fteachers and the wider school
OL,11,Fcommunity.
OL,13,F"The victim's family, and others
OL,14,Faffected by what happened, are being
OL,15,Foffered support.
OL,17,F"Detectives and uniformed officers
OL,18,Fhave worked quickly and I hope our
OL,19,Fresponse and these charges provide
OL,20,Fsome comfort to those impacted.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/6
